Ingredients
* 2 pounds beef chuck roast, cubed
* salt
* ground black pepper
* 4 ounces butter (or more)
* 2 sweet onions, sliced
* 4 tablespoons all-purpose flour
* 1 (10.5 ounce) can condensed beef broth
* 1 teaspoon prepared mustard
* 6 ounce sliced mushrooms
* 1/3 cup sour cream
* 1/3 cup white wine
* Pasta twisty noodles

Directions

Prepare beef
* add butter to large saucepan, melt
* add beef to pan with butter, salt and pepper
* brown beef, set aside in oven safe pot
* cook onions in butter, put with beef in oven safe pot
* add broth to the oven safe pot
* cook musrooms in butter
* add to the oven safe pot
* in pan add more butter if needed, add tablespoons of flour, whisk
* add mustard, whisk
* keep whisking and simmer 2 minutes
* mix roux into the oven safe pot

Prepare pasta
* cook pasta twisty noodles al-dente

Right before serving
* Add noodles, sour cream and white wine into the oven safe pot, heat for 5-10 minutes

Notes

Taken and modified from https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/25202/beef-stroganoff-iii/
